(227, '2017-12-14 15:10:00', '2017-12-14 15:10:00', 'Adlan', 'adlanhospital@gmail.om', '00971555953300', 'Inquiry', 'Searching for psychiatry care.', 'Dear Sir/Madam\r\n\r\nMy nephew is 22 years old, he has been diagnosed with OCD, mood disorder and unspecified psychotic symptoms.  He has been seen by local doctors for the last 3 years, Unfortunately, his case has not stabilized and he is still suffering from a number of psychotic symptoms that didnt resolve with all the treatments and medical care he received. I have attached a detailed information about his case and medication for the last 3 years, hoping that it will guide you in understanding the case.\r\n\r\nI writing to require if you have a specialized facility that has a good record in achieving better results in patients who have not made progress in their country to help my nephew resuming his life and studies in the future.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you\r\n\r\nDr Adlan Izzeldin', '1', NULL, NULL),
