(229, '2017-12-19 10:34:20', '2017-12-19 10:34:20', 'musa bojang', 'musabojang413@gmail.com', '01111907158', 'Inquiry', 'HLA typing', 'I want to make a test. I want to know if you do it and the price.\r\n\r\nCurrently we are searching a bonemarrow transplant donor for the Brother of Mr Bojang (Mohamed, born last year). Please perform HLA-Typing, to clearify if your patient Mr. Bojang could serve as a bmt-donor. Ideally 10/10 digit typing would be requested, as a minium HLA-A, B, C, DR and DQ should be analyzed. \r\nThe following HLA Antigens need to be studied:\r\n\r\nHLA-A\r\nHLA-B\r\nHLA-C\r\nHLA-DR\r\nHLA-DQ', '1', NULL, NULL),
