(238, '2018-01-03 13:29:08', '2018-01-03 13:29:08', 'Sanaa Sheikh', 's.sheikh@smd12.qmul.ac.uk', '07855442233', 'Inquiry', 'Elective ', 'I am a final year medical student from Barts and the London, soon approaching qualification as a Registered Doctor.  As part of our programme, all students must experience medicine in a clinical environment outside of the UK. The purpose of this is to provide a unique opportunity to explore medicine in an entirely new social and cultural environment.\r\n\r\nI am writing to you to enquire whether it would be possible for my colleague and I to complete our elective with yourselves. I would be grateful if you could provide access to an online application process in order to apply for a placement in internal medicine for an opportunity to immerse myself in medical practice in another country.\r\n\r\nThe dates for the placement are any period from 16th April to 7th May 2018.\r\n\r\nI acknowledge that all costs incurred with regard to the placement are my responsibility. \r\n \r\nLook forward to hearing from you soon with application details.\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1', NULL, NULL),
