(6, 'Overnight Stay', 'We are obliged to provide you the best facilities in terms of your stay with us.', '1526437215icon_overnight_stay.png', '<h5>Selecting Your Room</h5><p>We are obliged to provide you the best facilities in terms of your stay with us. The rooms of your choice are as follows:</p><ul><li>Single bedded  Superior</li><li>Single bedded  Standard</li><li>Double bedded</li><li>Double bedded  whole room</li><li>Four bedded</li></ul><p>All meals are complimentary to the patient and menu will be given to you daily to indicate your preference.</p><h5>What to Bring / What Not to Bring</h5><h6>Documents:</h6><ul><li>Identification documents (i.e. IC, Passport, Birth Certificate), Employer''s Letter of Guarantee / Health Card of which the company has an account with KPJ Sentosa KL Specialist Hospital.</li></ul><h6>Personal Items:</h6><ul><li>Personal clothing</li><li>Slippers / Toiletries</li></ul><h6>Deposit:</h6><p>You will be required to place a deposit upon admission. The deposit amount varies depending on the classification of case and treatment received. Additional deposit will be required when your expenses exceed the initial deposit paid.</p><h6>Valuables:</h6><p>Patients are advised against bringing and keeping valuables with them whenever in the hospital. The hospital, however shall not be responsible for any lost or damage to property while in our premises.</p><h6>Identification Bracelet:</h6><p>You will be given an identification wrist bracelet for identification purpose. Please do not remove this band during your stay in hospital.</p><h6>Meal Service:</h6><p>Meals served to the patient have both local and western cuisine. For any special diet needs, you can inform our nursing staff. If your treatment involves a special therapeutic diet, our hospital dietitian will visit you for dietary counseling.</p><p>Feel free to consult our Dietitian regarding your special diet.</p><h6>Nurse Call</h6><p>A nurse call bell is located near your bed and the bathroom. Please press the bell if you need any assistance.</p><h6>Hand Phone</h6><p>Hand phones are not allowed within the hospital premises where there iddds high frequency electronic equipment as they will interfere with the equipment.</p><h6>Parking</h6><p>Parking is available at the basement of the hospital building. Besides, you can also park you vehicle at Grand Season Hotel and you can get your parking ticket stamped at various counter for a flat rate of RM5.00.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Hospital', '2018-03-27 22:57:14', '2018-05-26 16:43:18', 1),
